videos.description: Kansas gets an easy bucket to get the crowd into the game early on.
videos.headline: Jayhawks earn points from Iowa State turnover

videos.description: Kansas is off and running in the first half against Iowa State.
videos.headline: Devonte' Graham lobs ball to Frank Mason III for 2

videos.description: A deflected pass bounces the Jayhawks' way as they build a lead on Iowa State.
videos.headline: Lagerald Vick slams in big dunk for Kansas

videos.description: F. Mason III made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by D. Graham.
videos.headline: Frank Mason III narrowly beats shot clock with three point jumper

videos.description: Mason remains perfect from the field as Kansas extends its second-half lead on Iowa State.
videos.headline: Frank Mason III sinks 3-point jumper from the corner

videos.description: M. Morris made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by D. Burton.
videos.headline: Monte Morris sinks three to help Iowa State close in on the Jayhawks' lead

videos.description: L. Vick made Dunk. Assisted by J. Jackson.
videos.headline: Lagerald Vick makes powerful dunk

videos.description: The Cyclones erased a 15-point deficit as Burton made his sixth trifecta of the game against Kansas.
videos.headline: Deonte Burton makes 3-pointer to give Iowa State a lead

videos.description: The Cyclones scored the first five points of the overtime period against Kansas.
videos.headline: Deonte Burton hits 3-pointer to extend Iowa State's OT lead

videos.description: D. Burton made Three Point Jumper. Assisted by M. Morris.
videos.headline: Deonte Burton hits three pointer to extend Iowa State's overtime lead

videos.description: Iowa State overcomes a 14-point halftime deficit to defeat No. 3 Kansas in overtime 92-89, ending the Jayhawks' 54-game home winning streak.
videos.headline: Iowa State rallies to topple No. 3 Kansas in OT
